---------------------------------------------------
Release 1.3		Lib Version 3.1.1

	18 October, 2005
	MODIFIED View *ViewFactory::decorateView(View *returnview, const char *decoratorname)
		Moved things around in a better order.


-------------
--------------------------
---------------------------------------------------
Release 1.2		Lib Version 3.0.1

	02 September, 2005
	Made View::getCharset() virtual.  setCharset and getCharset are now
	chained through the Decorator into the decorated View.  This way,
	The View has the opportunity to set the charset itself...



-------------
--------------------------
---------------------------------------------------
Release 1.1		Lib Version 2.0.1

	19 July, 2005
	** Added Decorator::insertDecorator(const char *decoratorname)
	Allows a decorator to defer decoration to another decorator....

-------------
--------------------------
---------------------------------------------------
Release 1.0		Lib Version 1.0.0

	Converted to Open Source project

